snippet.title: Dark Traveller - Third Person Shooter Puzzle - Gameplay (PC)
snippet.description:
Dark Traveller is an action-packed puzzle game with multiple storylines and open endings. The game tells the story of a world on the brink of apocalypse in the distant future. 

If you are a dev and want me to delete a video of your game just email me and I'll delet it asap.
contatopobregamer@gmail.com

PC Settings:
GPU - ASUS Dual Radeon RX 6600 XT OC Driver: 23.2.2
CPU - RYZEN 5 5600 Stock
Motherboard B450M GAMING (rev. 1.x)
RAM: 2X8 3200MHZ
2X SSD 240GB
1X M.2 NVME 512GB
WIN 10
